The third day prayer for late Alhaji Abba Yusufu holds today at his residence, Babban Gida, Adoro Quarters in Katsina at 11am, his son, Nasir Abba Yusuf, said yesterday. Yusufu, a cousin of the chairman of Media Trust Limited, Malam Kabiru Yusuf, died Thursday night after a brief illness. Aged 90, he is survived by a wife and 13 children. Sympathizers have been visiting the family to condole with them. They include Governor Mohammed Abdullahi Abubakar of Bauchi State and his wife Hadiza, the wife of Katsina State governor Hadiza Masari, the District Head of Safana and Yariman Katsina, Sada Rufai.